Description: Multi-dimensional array of NetCDF files
DescDetail: <<
This package allows Octave to access a single netCDF file or a collection
of such files as a multi-dimensional array.

It provides the following functions:
ncArray:
        ncArray
        ncCatArray
        nccoord
        cached_decompress
        @ncArray/coord
        @ncArray/ncArray
        @ncArray/subsasgn
        @ncArray/subsref
ncBaseArray:
        @BaseArray/BaseArray
        @BaseArray/end
        @BaseArray/full
        @BaseArray/isnumeric
        @BaseArray/max
        @BaseArray/mean
        @BaseArray/min
        @BaseArray/moment
        @BaseArray/numel
        @BaseArray/prod
        @BaseArray/reduce
        @BaseArray/size
        @BaseArray/std
        @BaseArray/sum
        @BaseArray/sumsq
        @BaseArray/var
Test script:
        test_ncarray
<<

